                        band; geometric, floral and zoomorphic motifs (birds).</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d2">- <locus target="#38ra">38ra</locus>: two
                        simple coloured (red and black) ornamental bands; floral and zoomorphic
                        motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d3">- <locus target="#38va">38va-</locus>b-c
                        (explicit of Text I): three elaborate coloured (red, black, yellow)
                        ornamental bands; geometric, floral and zoomorphic motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">- <locus target="#39ra">39ra-</locus>b-c
                        (incipit of Text II): elaborate coloured (red, black, yellow) ornamental
                        band; geometric, floral, zoomorphic and anthropomorphic motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d5">- <locus target="#104rc">104rc</locus>:
