                        floral motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d6">- <locus target="#125ra">125ra-</locus>b
                        (explicit of Text II): two elaborate coloured (red, black, yellow)
                        ornamental bands; geometric, floral and zoomorphic motifs.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
